com.intuit.wasabi.tests.library.util

Annotation Type RetryTest


  • @Documented
 @Target(value=METHOD)
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface RetryTest
    An annotation to allow retrials of @Test methods. Testmethods should be annotated similar to this to be retried multiple times: 
     
  {@literal @}Test
  {@literal @}RetryTest(maxTries="5", timeout="0")
   public void myTestMethod() {
       ...
   }
